Package: tabexp
Title: Creating a table of births and exposure from a DHS-like birth history
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Bruno", "Schoumaker", , "bruno.schoumaker@uclouvain.be", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: tabexp creates a table of births and exposure from a DHS-like birth history. By default, it uses the variable names of the DHS. Weights and all-women factors are used. The table can be used to compte ASFRs.
